Exercise

-Think about how would you modify your model created for the ION Solid
application in order to get it created by spring using dependency injection.
How would the xml or the annotations look like?

-Think about the ION Solid application, do you have a web presentation? How
would you change your current application implementation to use Spring
MVC as the main web framework for implementing the presentation? Do this
change at least to handle 1 request and demonstrate Spring MVC in action.

